<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>عبد الرحمن <span class="c2">(١٠)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>إسمعيل <span class="c2">(١١)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>يوسف <span class="c2">(١٢)</span>، مات سنة ٦٥٦ وله ٨٩<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>عبد السلام <span class="c2">(١٣)</span>، مات سنة ٦٠٥، وله ٨٥<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
